1213
01:08:58,360 --> 01:09:01,360
 But it's great to come home and feel like
 you've made a contribution, isn't it?

1214
01:09:02,600 --> 01:09:03,799
 Yes, of course.

1215
01:09:03,800 --> 01:09:05,519
 Or not, as the case may be.

1216
01:09:05,520 --> 01:09:07,399
 Oh, l'm sure you contribute.

1217
01:09:07,400 --> 01:09:10,159
 Not me. l'm talking about you lot
 in the caring professions.

1218
01:09:10,160 --> 01:09:11,719
 - l don't care.
 - We know.

1219
01:09:11,720 --> 01:09:13,959
 Hard man.

1220
01:09:13,960 --> 01:09:16,960
 And l know you're a geologist, Tom,
 but what exactly do you do?

1221
01:09:17,480 --> 01:09:20,480
