1227
01:09:31,320 --> 01:09:34,320
 l call it a trailer-mounted-tripod
 cable-percussive boring unit.

1228
01:09:36,320 --> 01:09:37,999
 And that's why l love him.

1229
01:09:38,000 --> 01:09:40,119
 No, l investigate
 the ground beneath our feet

1230
01:09:40,120 --> 01:09:43,120
 to test the feasibility of various
 engineering and building projects.

1231
01:09:43,400 --> 01:09:45,919
 lt sounds amazing. What are you
 working on at the moment?

1232
01:09:45,920 --> 01:09:48,920
