01:16:02,320 --> 01:16:05,320
 What makes you think l'm a secretary?

1381
01:16:05,600 --> 01:16:07,559
 Well, you are, aren't you?

1382
01:16:07,560 --> 01:16:10,560
 - Gerri said...
