1383
01:16:11,800 --> 01:16:13,839
 Well...

1384
01:16:13,840 --> 01:16:15,999
 l got my diploma. l look after the doctors.

1385
01:16:16,000 --> 01:16:18,479
 Oh, brilliant.

1386
01:16:18,480 --> 01:16:21,039
 So have you two worked together
 for a long time?

1387
01:16:21,040 --> 01:16:23,319
 Ooh, about 20 years, haven't we, Mary?

1388
01:16:23,320 --> 01:16:24,319
 Yeah.

1389
01:16:24,320 --> 01:16:27,279
 - Mary's known Joe since he was ten.
