1394
01:16:37,640 --> 01:16:39,279
 She's almost like an auntie to him.

1395
01:16:39,280 --> 01:16:40,639
 l wouldn't say that.

1396
01:16:40,640 --> 01:16:42,439
 Well, we think of you as his auntie.

1397
01:16:42,440 --> 01:16:43,879
 Auntie Mary.

1398
01:16:43,880 --> 01:16:46,879
 l think that's really sweet.

1399
01:16:46,880 --> 01:16:49,880
 - Right. Who wants some cake?
 - Yes, please.

1400
01:16:54,040 --> 01:16:55,599
 Auntie Mary.

1401
01:16:55,600 --> 01:16:58,199
 Thanks, Joe.

1402
01:16:58,200 --> 01:17:00,759
 Thanks, Mum.

1403
01:17:00,760 --> 01:17:03,079
 lt must be really boring looking after old people.

1404
01:17:03,080 --> 01:17:04,719
 No, l love it.

1405
01:17:04,720 --> 01:17:07,720
 You get to know them really well
 and, well...

1406
01:17:08,680 --> 01:17:10,919
 ..we're all going to be old, one day,
