1407
01:17:10,920 --> 01:17:12,479
 Touch wood.

1408
01:17:12,480 --> 01:17:15,480
 TOM: Some of us already are.
 - (Katie giggles)

1409
01:17:16,640 --> 01:17:19,359
 We look after old people, don't we, Gerri?

1410
01:17:19,360 --> 01:17:22,360
 No, not in the same way.

1411
01:17:28,440 --> 01:17:29,919
 Amazing cake.

1412
01:17:29,920 --> 01:17:32,920
 Thank you, Katie.

1413
01:17:37,400 --> 01:17:38,479
 TOM:
 Right.

1414
01:17:38,480 --> 01:17:40,239
 We'll see you when we see you.

1415
01:17:40,240 --> 01:17:42,639
 - Soon. Hopefully.
 - And you'll never know when.

1416
01:17:42,640 --> 01:17:45,640
 - Probably find you hiding in the shed.
