1419
01:17:49,640 --> 01:17:52,239
 l hear you're both excellent cooks. No pressure.

1420
01:17:52,240 --> 01:17:54,519
 - Tom makes a mean curry.
 - Oh, l love curry.

1421
01:17:54,520 --> 01:17:57,520
 - Well, there's been no litigation to date.
 - l'll take my chances, then.

1422
01:17:58,320 --> 01:17:59,759
 - l'll speak to you later.
 - Bye.

1423
01:17:59,760 --> 01:18:01,439
 - See you, boy.
 - Bye-bye. Take care.

1424
01:18:01,440 --> 01:18:03,679
 - Thank you so much.
