1426
01:18:05,840 --> 01:18:07,959
 Bye, Mary. Really nice to meet you.

1427
01:18:07,960 --> 01:18:09,919
 Hope you get your car sorted out.

1428
01:18:09,920 --> 01:18:11,519
 - Bye, Katie.
 - Bye.

1429
01:18:11,520 --> 01:18:13,479
 TOM: Bye.
 KATlE: See you soon.

1430
01:18:13,480 --> 01:18:15,479
 TOM: Yeah. Safe journey. Bye.
 - Bye.

1431
01:18:15,480 --> 01:18:17,199
 (front door closes)

1432
01:18:17,200 --> 01:18:18,959
 How about that, then?

1433
01:18:18,960 --> 01:18:21,959
 - That's a turn-up for the books.
