 Carl, we've got loads ofwine.

1723
01:37:05,240 --> 01:37:08,240
 Carl.

1724
01:37:11,440 --> 01:37:14,440
 He won't be back.

1725
01:37:18,200 --> 01:37:21,200
 Pyjamas. Get some shirts.

