01:37:23,000 --> 01:37:25,359
 - Are you going to change?
 - Yeah.

1727
01:37:25,360 --> 01:37:28,360
 - Do you want this?
 - Yeah.

1728
01:37:47,640 --> 01:37:49,719
 How you doing?

1729
01:37:49,720 --> 01:37:51,359
 Are you all right?

1730
01:37:51,360 --> 01:37:54,360
 Yeah, l'll be all right.

1731
01:37:54,560 --> 01:37:57,560
 We'll be off soon.

1732
