01:40:46,400 --> 01:40:48,599
 Ronnie. Tom's my brother.

1759
01:40:48,600 --> 01:40:51,599
 Oh, oh.

1760
01:40:51,600 --> 01:40:54,600
 ls it your wife that's just passed away?

