01:50:14,480 --> 01:50:17,480
 l might have to have a little bit of a lie down.

1876
01:50:23,960 --> 01:50:26,960
 lt's really lovely
 to have someone to talk to.

1877
01:50:29,440 --> 01:50:32,440
 Yeah.

1878
01:50:34,440 --> 01:50:37,440
 lt's peaceful here.

1879
01:50:43,200 --> 01:50:46,200
 l might move away somewhere else.

