01:50:48,160 --> 01:50:51,160
 Start again.

1881
01:50:53,120 --> 01:50:56,120
 l used to work in Majorca.

1882
01:51:06,000 --> 01:51:09,000
 They'll be back soon.

1883
01:51:10,600 --> 01:51:13,600
 Oh, yeah.

1884
01:51:28,000 --> 01:51:31,000
 - There you go.
 - Thank you.

1885
01:51:36,360 --> 01:51:39,360
 (low conversation, door opens)

1886
01:51:41,920 --> 01:51:43,719
 (laughter)

1887
01:51:43,720 --> 01:51:46,359
 - Hello, Ronnie.
 - We're back.

1888
01:51:46,360 --> 01:51:49,359
 Hi, Gerri.

1889
01:51:49,360 --> 01:51:51,319
 - Hello, Mary.
 - Bloody hell!

1890
01:51:51,320 --> 01:51:54,320
 - Hi, Tom.
 - What are you doing here?

1891
01:51:55,160 --> 01:51:58,160
 Well, l just thought l'd...

1892
01:52:01,440 --> 01:52:04,440
 Just get my boots off.

1893
01:52:04,640 --> 01:52:07,599
 - Where'd she spring from?
 - Bloody nuisance, especially today.

1894
01:52:07,600 --> 01:52:10,600
 You're not kidding.

1895
01:52:17,000 --> 01:52:19,319
 (sighs)

1896
01:52:19,320 --> 01:52:22,320
 - Are you all right, Gerri?
 - Yes, Mary, l'm fine.

1897
01:52:27,160 --> 01:52:28,719
 Did you drive?

1898
01:52:28,720 --> 01:52:30,679
 Oh, no. l came on the tube.

1899
01:52:30,680 --> 01:52:33,680
 Did you?

1900
01:52:34,080 --> 01:52:36,399
 lt might have been nice
 if you'd phoned first, Mary.

1901
01:52:36,400 --> 01:52:39,400
 Oh, l'm really sorry.

1902
01:52:46,000 --> 01:52:49,000
 - Joe and Katie are coming.
 - Yeah, Ronnie said.

1903
01:52:56,560 --> 01:52:59,560
 All righty.

1904
01:52:59,880 --> 01:53:02,880
 TOM: Tea, Ronnie?
 - Yeah.

1905
01:53:08,640 --> 01:53:11,640
 GERRl: Come and sit yourself down, Mary,
