1907
01:53:22,520 --> 01:53:25,520
 (channels change)

1908
01:53:38,800 --> 01:53:40,839
 How's it going?

1909
01:53:40,840 --> 01:53:42,839
 lnexorably.

1910
01:53:42,840 --> 01:53:45,840
 - l don't know what to do.
 - Well, if you don't, l don't.

1911
01:53:46,280 --> 01:53:48,919
 l can't just chuck her out.

1912
01:53:48,920 --> 01:53:50,839
 - Can't you?
 - No.

1913
01:53:50,840 --> 01:53:53,840
 - Look at the state of her.
 - l know. Poor woman.

1914
01:53:55,360 --> 01:53:57,679
 Joe and Katie will be all right.
 They can handle her.

1915
01:53:57,680 --> 01:54:00,239
 l know. l've got enough food for her.

1916
01:54:00,240 --> 01:54:03,240
 - That's all right, then.
 - Oh, well, here goes.

1917
01:54:07,480 --> 01:54:10,480
 (approaching footsteps)

1918
01:54:18,200 --> 01:54:21,200
 - Do you want me to give you a hand?
 - No, thank you, Mary.

1919
01:54:24,200 --> 01:54:26,119
 Would you like to stay for a bite to eat?

1920
01:54:26,120 --> 01:54:28,039
 No, it's OK. l don't want to be in the way.

1921
01:54:28,040 --> 01:54:31,040
 You won't be. We've got plenty offood.

1922
01:54:32,160 --> 01:54:34,759
 Are you still angry with me?

1923
01:54:34,760 --> 01:54:37,760
 Mary, l wasn't angry with you.
 l just felt you'd let me down.

1924
01:54:38,680 --> 01:54:41,680
 Oh, Gerri.

1925
01:54:41,760 --> 01:54:44,760
 l'd never want to do that.

1926
01:54:45,800 --> 01:54:47,279
 l'm really sorry.

1927
01:54:47,280 --> 01:54:50,280
 Yes, and l know you apologised.

1928
01:54:56,200 --> 01:54:59,200
 l miss you.

1929
01:54:59,320 --> 01:55:01,399
 l mean, l know l see you at work,

1930
01:55:01,400 --> 01:55:04,400
 but we don't seem to talk to each other
 any more.

1931
01:55:06,480 --> 01:55:09,480
 - l feel terrible.
 - This is my family, Mary.

1932
01:55:09,840 --> 01:55:11,719
 You've got to understand that.

1933
01:55:11,720 --> 01:55:14,720
 (sobs):
 l do.

1934
01:55:15,440 --> 01:55:18,440
 Oh... Come here.

1935
01:55:24,840 --> 01:55:27,840
 (Mary sobs)

1936
01:55:37,640 --> 01:55:40,399
 You have to take responsibility
 for your actions.

1937
01:55:40,400 --> 01:55:43,400
 l know.

1938
01:55:47,680 --> 01:55:50,680
 Now, listen, Mary.

1939
01:55:51,920 --> 01:55:54,239
 You need to talk to somebody.

1940
01:55:54,240 --> 01:55:57,239
 Oh, no, l don't want to do that.

1941
01:55:57,240 --> 01:56:00,240
 - Well, l think it would help you.
 - l just want to talk to you.

